
Ranger Help for: enemy cow
==========================

SUMMARY:
Choosing cow means your Ranger specializes against cattle, aurochs, oxen,
and similar herd animals.

This is a narrower enemy choice, but it can matter in plains, underground
areas, farms, and places where large horned herd creatures are common.

COMMAND:
  setenemy cow

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
